{"tid":451140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[巨乳人妻]澳洲婦胸部長不停　望出國縮胸可再次跑步","createTime":"2017-10-29T00:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T11:54:05.000Z","uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc298b6d04d4f6d1589d9588057ebf2e24672329","tid":451140,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T00:09:15.000Z","msg":"澳洲一名婦人自發育以來，胸部的發展便持續不停。但豐腴的身材為她帶來無比煩惱，因為嚴重妨礙生活，基本如跑步都難。儘管現時已身為人母，胸部已停止發育，但礙於資金問題，女子一直未有做手術縮胸。她希望可以出國做手術，與子女享受奔跑的樂趣。 <br />\n<br />\n來自維多利亞省的23歲媽媽拉克曼（Sheridan Larkman）由8歲起，胸部已急速「成長」，至10歲已達傲人的DD罩杯。但拉克曼對此非常困擾，非但被男同學嘲笑，而且需要束胸令她才可以踢波及跳舞。16歲時，拉克曼已擁有H罩杯，但卻使她痛苦不已，因為胸部的重量引發各種痛症。她曾經問醫生自己的情況是否正常，對方指一切是女性必經的過程。 <br />\n<br />\n到18歲意外懷孕後，拉克曼的胸部甚至一度漲大至JJ罩杯。她的痛苦亦隨之增加，曾經試過胸罩不抵胸部的重量彈出，鋼圈刺傷自己。拉克曼表示：「當我站立時，背及頸部都承受巨大壓力，不自覺地向前俯身減重，令我看起來似個駝背的人。」在誕下次女後，拉克曼的胸部更是高達K罩杯。 <br />\n<br />\n然而，由於在澳洲做縮胸手術索價達1.4萬澳元（約8.4萬港元），拉克曼難以負擔。她希望可以出國做手術縮胸，可以與兩名女兒一同自由奔跑。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171029/mobile/bknint-20171029000055987-1029_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171029%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20171029000055987-1029_17011_001.html&d=Itfvph%2BQOrl1vKl0YnMCVMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=55689c29\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171029/mobile/bknint-20171029000055987-1029_17011_001.html</a><br />\n入面有圖"},{"pid":"1aab732766c66462ebca5d71cff26d09bfc2429e","tid":451140,"uid":151728,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T00:13:45.000Z","msg":"你試下再亂用tag"},{"pid":"0f6700786fafae35208b6786b8ca685ddec5a6f0","tid":451140,"uid":8048,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T00:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PRTDzvG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPRTDzvG.jpg&h=c59f6669&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f6352dd404ebd3377d42724f95125ef0ac53fec","tid":451140,"uid":322,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T00:17:29.000Z","msg":"根本就係肥"},{"pid":"47afdb03b48309cc297a7428bfd6ea31195c4b7f","tid":451140,"uid":58071,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T00:19:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a661c8135d80f51ae3c255ad125bb3952cb46724","tid":451140,"uid":55386,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T00:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就係肥</blockquote><br />\n肥婆唔肯減肥真係寧舍多借口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dc2606299f3ba670ab4bbed39b6f30624303d3","tid":451140,"uid":132038,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T00:47:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b36ded652fa5198a0bb99ea3cfd98a9338b01dd","tid":451140,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PRTDzvG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPRTDzvG.jpg&h=c59f6669&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢張圖幾耐歷史"},{"pid":"6371e651008b0ef049a23c87bb44c96a2aa21c4c","tid":451140,"uid":70985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"仲未入黎"},{"pid":"7a029154ddf0fbf011b4bfc8db29624bf1945547","tid":451140,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7c3241305c4bfde30ed404416ec3bbee1ba854","tid":451140,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:31:33.000Z","msg":"鬼婆真係好易殘，由其生左之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa48ac16d2fc8777558f09838a168b1b4a7079e","tid":451140,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":